data.description: This modular home has lots of extras! 3 bedrooms/4 full bathrooms. Main floor: primary bedroom with full bath and walk-in closet, guest room, living room with gas log fireplace, kitchen, dining area, laundry room, access to screened in covered porch, fixed attic stairs. Attic is unfinished and is currently being used for storage, wired and plumbed to possibly add more square footage. Basement has a bedroom, full bathroom, kitchen, living room area with gas logs, dining or office area, unfinished storage room and an unfinished workroom. Basement has inside and outside entrance. The heated garage has a full bath inside of it. Steps going to attic from garage for extra storage. There is a detached garage/building in the backyard that would be great to store yard equipment in, electricity is ran to it. 220. Needs some new floor covering and fresh paint, make it your own! Lots of extras in this home. Propane tank is leased. Beautiful views! Come out and see this home! Being sold as is.
